message.content: black and beige kitchen cabinets and countertop; refrigerator behind the cabinets; four white chairs around a wooden table in a dining area; box of crackers, plastic bottle of water and disposable plastic cups on the table; sink in the kitchen counter; wooden framed mirror on the wall above the sink; range hood above the stove; food items on the countertop including two jars with a label, boxes of jello, rice bubbles and crackers, and a cup. The environment has white walls, dark wood flooring, and a round light fixture on the ceiling. The kitchen area is on one side of the room, and the dining area is on the other side. The objects are positioned on the kitchen counter, on the table, and on the floor.
